title: Aidan Burrell
text:
Aidan Burrell (born 3 August 2003) is an English professional <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> footballer who plays as a for <a href="Hull%20F.C.">Hull FC</a> in the <a href="Betfred%20Super%20League">Betfred Super League</a>.
In 2021 he made his <a href="Hull%20F.C.">FC</a> debut in the <a href="Super%20League">Super League</a> against the <a href="Huddersfield%20Giants">Huddersfield Giants</a>.
